data.value:
Features of the Application
1] Product Management: Easily add, update, or remove products from inventory.
2] Sales Reports: View sales trends with dynamic reporting tools.
3] User-Friendly Interface: Intuitive design for easy navigation.
4] Customer Management: Maintain a database of customer information and purchase history.
5] Real-Time Inventory Tracking: Monitor stock levels with low inventory notifications.
